      "rationale": "Four-level mesh convergence study performed on the screw-rod assembly. Global element size reduced from 1.5 mm to 0.4 mm. Richardson extrapolation applied; GCI for stiffness QoI is 1.3%. Final mesh of 287,000 elements selected. Discretization error estimated at 1.1% of QoI, well within acceptance bound."
