    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The FEA model ensemble meets quantitative acceptance criteria for all three QoIs across N=11 specimens at two laboratories. E/uval values below 1.96 and percent differences below 10% for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement. One factor (Test conditions) achieved below required level, acknowledged as a credibility gap with scope limitation documented. Two factors (Relevance of QoIs; Relevance of validation activities to COU) were not assessed due to resource and scope constraints — considered acceptable by the team given the standard test method context, though these gaps are noted. Overall credibility judged sufficient for a Medium assurance level decision at modelRiskLevel 3.",
